{"tid":2430402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年逾 2,100 大專生退學　16 年來最多　理大生佔近四分一","createTime":"2021-03-03T02:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T03:37:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a892fe8495d7898001d4978daee89fece49cf840","tid":2430402,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"大學資助教育委員會（教資會）發表 2019/20 年度年報，八大院校各級課程共錄得 2,121 人終止學業（下簡稱退學），數字創 16 年最高。退學者中有 1,804 人正就讀學士學位課程，整體學士生退學比例為 2.1 %，同為 16 年來最高。八大院校中，以理工大學的退學人數最多，各級共計 505 人退學，佔整體退學人數近 24 %。<br />\n<br />\n教資會最新統計數字於去年 12 月更新，只計算學士生退學人數，除了教育大學之外，另外 7 間教資會資助大學的退學人數均錄得升幅，其中以理大的升幅較為顯著。在 2018/19 年度，理大共有 224 名學士生退學，佔該年該校學士生的 1.5%；至 2019/20 年度，理大學士生退學人數升至 329 人，比例亦升 0.7 個百分點，至 2.2%。<br />\n<br />\n港大、科大退學人數亦增<br />\n<br />\n除理大之外，港大、中大的退學人數亦有上升。其中，香港大學在 2019/20 年度有 343 名學士生退學，佔整體學士生的 2.0%，較上一年度增加 0.5 個百分點；科大則有 207 名學士生退學，比例約 2.1%，同樣較上一年度增加 0.5 個分點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%BE-2-100-%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%88%E7%94%9F%E9%80%80%E5%AD%B8-16-%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BD%94%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2580%25BE-2-100-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%2588%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%25AD%25B8-16-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=bdc584fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2580%25BE-2-100-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%2588%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%25AD%25B8-16-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%2F&h=2e3e3d21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%BE-2-100-%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%88%E7%94%9F%E9%80%80%E5%AD%B8-16-%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BD%94%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80/</a>"},{"pid":"69437f7965d69c75f5ae6b02c5b24af02413efb3","tid":2430402,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"支支退學？"},{"pid":"f0ed0442a25ddb3575d46efe3591eaafa7021828","tid":2430402,"uid":365765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"69437f7965d69c75f5ae6b02c5b24af02413efb3","tid":2430402,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"支支退學？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"似去外國讀"},{"pid":"d2407c6051a22f0953b07fed2874f7b36be405af","tid":2430402,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"班校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16f7a512cb05629ad04cb85721ec8e930f98686","tid":2430402,"uid":6777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"升左 0.幾都拎黎講"},{"pid":"70805f58fa7f2d26a054fd042e8024a4568b681e","tid":2430402,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"4年後都唔知似乜啦<br />\n點係度讀"},{"pid":"aba9dbc7df956f4208ad2f19158e446eef6be75f","tid":2430402,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"去加拿大或英國啦<br />\n<br />\n仲留係度把柒咩"},{"pid":"e3efbb2c243ba0b6693716978c78d09c4e89c535","tid":2430402,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"有得揀都唔係香港讀啦"},{"pid":"724ceb4bfb90dc342900aeea0aba7fd9fc9dfa37","tid":24304